FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our food-building app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: 'Building Foods' is an innovative app that allows you to create custom food items by combining various ingredients and cooking techniques. It's like Lego, but for food!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply select your base ingredients, choose cooking methods, and add flavors or toppings. The app guides you through the process and provides recipes for your unique food creations.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I share my food creations with others?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! You can share your culinary masterpieces on the app's community feed, and even collaborate with other food builders to create exciting new dishes.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the app suitable for beginners?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, the app is designed for all skill levels. We offer tutorials, tips, and safety guidelines to help beginners start their food-building journey with confidence.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Are there any dietary options available?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Of course! You can filter ingredients and recipes based on various dietary preferences, including vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, and more. Build foods that suit your lifestyle!
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Food Building
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Food building is an innovative concept where users can create custom meals by selecting and combining various ingredients using our app. It's like constructing a delicious masterpiece from the ground up!
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Our app provides a user-friendly interface where you can choose from a wide range of ingredients, customize portions, and experiment with flavor combinations. Simply select your desired components and watch as your meal comes together virtually before preparing it in real life.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I save my food creations?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! You can save all your unique food builds in the app for future reference. This feature allows you to easily recreate your favorite combinations or share them with friends and family.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app suitable for dietary restrictions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our app caters to various dietary needs. You can filter ingredients based on specific requirements such as vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, or low-carb options, ensuring that your food builds align with your dietary preferences or restrictions.
